 ('2', '2', 'en_us', 'Welcome to Costello!', '<p>It’s true, this site doesn’t have a whole lot of content yet, but don’t worry. Our web developers have just installed the CMS, and they’re setting things up for the content editors this very moment. Soon Costello will be an oasis of fresh perspectives, sharp analyses, and astute opinions that will keep you coming back again and again.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-20 18:51:51', '2017-07-20 18:51:51', '00509a48-ccef-4096-924f-d0d14f9e2fad'),
 ('7', '7', 'en_us', 'Bio', NULL, '<p>Costello is a psychedelic / garage / experimental rock group from Norman, OK.<br /><br />In fall of 2016 they reunited with engineers Sam Welchel and Chad Copelin of Blackwatch Studios to record their sophomore album, “Conscious Trip.”<br /><br />The band consists of guitarist, vocalist and lyricist Clare Costello, bassist Felix Rodriguez and Flaming Lips drummer Matt Duckworth. The same crew, with a different drummer (Jason Scott) recorded their debut album “Manifest” in summer of 2015.</p>', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-07-28 18:40:59', '2017-10-11 04:28:30', 'c34a7fef-8364-43c7-8698-a71d12e34687'),
